entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! We just got word that you were not the only one hit. Another wing has been hit extremely hard and need support. Once you get the location get over there and help them out.
entries.title: Endor System: Destroy the Rebel Ambush
entries.title_d: The Rebel menace in the Endor system seems to have returned. Destroy all attacking vessels.
